title: WEDNESDAY - Blake Shelton breaks down TNF 2020
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY - Blake Shelton breaks down TNF 2020
description:
The Bears hurting at the quarterback position (0:07) as we bring you the latest on Nick Foles and his injured hip. Thursday Night Football (0:52) will see a big-time NFC West showdown between two big-time quarterbacks in Russell Wilson and Kyler Murray. Country music superstar and die-hard Cardinals fan Blake Shelton joined GMFB and gave his thoughts on the game (2:31). He also professed his love for the show and told Kay and the guys where it ranks on his list of lifetime achievements (3:52)
